description: California criminals are now targeting fire hydrants. About 100 hydrants have been stolen in Los Angeles County this year. Locks are now being added to hydrants to prevent the theft.
title: LA thieves target unlikely item, leaving communities at risk of suffering out-of-control fires

description: Time magazine's Massimo Calabresi told CNN's Jake Tapper that Biden in person is just as old as he appears to be on-screen, and has notably aged during his presidency.
title: Biden interviewer tells Tapper he's no different in person than on TV: Clearly 'older than when he started'
